   <abstract>This image shows Barbara Lair with a leash in both hands one holding a pony named Little Boy Blue, and a dog named Mr. Chips. Recto reads: Three Renfro Valley Pals, Renfro Valley, Ky. - 87-D-5. Verso reads: Barbara Lair, with Little Boy Blue and Mr. Chips, in front of the Lair Stable. Little Boy Blue has one more than 100 Blue Ribbons and Trophies for his little mistress and is considered one of the best Shetland ponies showing today.</abstract>
